thread.title: BRIEF- Shandong Intco Medical Products sees Q1 2018 net profit up 8.1 pct to 22.9 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF- Shandong Intco Medical Products sees Q1 2018 net profit up 8.1 pct to 22.9 pct

organizations.name: shandong intco medical products co ltd

text:
Feb 28(Reuters) - Shandong Intco Medical Products Co Ltd
* Sees Q1 2018 net profit to increase by 8.1 percent to 22.9 percent, or to be 22 million yuan to 25 million yuan
* Says Q1 2017 net profit was 20.4 million yuan
* Says that increased production capacity and sales, and exchange loss as main reasons for the forecast
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/WoUy7K
